  "merge_notes": "All three cards are from ICT school; no school conflict. One card (Education - ICT) includes Silver Bullet framework specifics, which are preserved. Another card (The Foundation) explicitly states that if SMT is present, Turtle Soup can be skipped; this nuance is included. Definitions were synthesized to include both the mechanism (sweep and close back inside) and the role as first step in reversal sequence.",
